     Then dot product is calculated as dot product = a1 * b1 + a2 * b2 + a3 * b3
     cross product = (a2 * b3 – a3 * b2) * i + (a3 * b1 – a1 * b3) * j + (a1 * b2 – a2 * b1) * k,
      where [(a2 * b3 – a3 * b2), (a3 * b1 – a1 * b3), (a1 * b2 – a2 * b1)] are the coefficient of
